# Starseed Station — commit ONLY what is needed to RUN the game:
#   index.html + css/shared.css + js/shared.js + sprites/ (PNG/JPG exports).
# Everything below is source art, dev tooling, docs, or OS junk.

# Source art — the game loads the PNG/JPG exports, never these
*.psd
**/originals/

# Dev/build pages, design docs, and tooling — not needed to run
demos/
resources/
CLAUDE.md

# Sprite-sheet coordinate dumps (dev artifacts; the sheets themselves are PNGs)
sprites/**/*.json

# Stray / OS junk
undefined/
.DS_Store
.vscode/
